{"tid":150443,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"原來 HKU 會收 IVE Year1","createTime":"2017-03-10T05:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T16:41:34.000Z","uid":14170,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dda68acd4f123b5b58111bd06c9d76297726e0a","tid":150443,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"話說我當年讀哂兩年 HD 先入大學，當年我係 HKU 收既第一批 IVE 仔之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我入 year1，但係 ENGG1111 PHYS1050 對讀過 AL 既人黎講只係入門水平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我當時 GPA 相當高<br />\n<br />\n然後，HKU 下一年竟然破格收 IVE 仔入 Year3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明以前剩係得 Space 可以直入 Senior Year <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再下一年，我收到風有個 Year1 IVE 仔 Sem1 GPA 4.0 直接上 HKU BEng Year1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌那星咁咪屈機過 ASSO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年我聽到青大 Year1 Sem1 3.9 已經收到 HKU Offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faa007656c45cc592bd1aca50ee64f1f9992b90","tid":150443,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"IVE DSE 收分低啲 (ASSO 高兩三分)<br />\nIVE 重實作 (好撚多實作 Project 做)，但考試既理論淺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (同一科 ASSO 啲內容深 2-30%)<br />\nIVE 畢業大把 consultant contractor 公司請做 Assistant Engineer (ASSO 畢業唔當你讀過工程)<br />\n<br />\nIVE 3.7 畢業可以入 HKU (ASSO 要 3.5)<br />\n依家連 Year1 Sem1 3.9 都入到 HKU (ASSO 要 3.8)"},{"pid":"7dff11a61d22afd8fb02b4f74cc552aae4f716ca","tid":150443,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"Ive 亞洲排第幾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5dfe76378735e5d379656d021f853e87a22694","tid":150443,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"而且 IVE 學費 七萬<br />\n包五個學期，仲會介紹多份 intern + grad job 比學生做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nASSO 十萬起跳<br />\n兩年四個學期，入到 U 都少 IVE 仔一份 intern 經驗，入唔到 U 連工都搵唔到"},{"pid":"8c6927a9a8e3b28af9736cebf49eaecadd21461d","tid":150443,"uid":55266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"2016 Space year 1 18個入番hku，禾相信禾將會下年入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c47f550666f78b012ac29b04a81f8b4f107e8f","tid":150443,"uid":59443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"到底每年收左幾多廣告費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adf9b56f8358708c2b6782a136a512b67feb546","tid":150443,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2016 Space year 1 18個入番hku，禾相信禾將會下年入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIVE year1 -&gt; HKU 2個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060f9f38927b39c16cd993a438e48dd991ae080d","tid":150443,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ive 亞洲排第幾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb9d6ba347ba59a0108e6a741f9085d3d4eb800","tid":150443,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2016 Space year 1 18個入番hku，禾相信禾將會下年入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIVE year1 -&gt; HKU 2個 <img src=\"/asset